snippet.title: Shin Megami Tensei V – Release Date Trailer | E3 2021
snippet.description:
Check out world premiere gameplay footage for the long-awaited Shin Megami Tensei V, launching exclusively for Nintendo Switch on 11/12. Nintendo Direct

Pre-orders begin 6/21: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/shin-megami-tensei-v-switch/
